#: docs/admin/50.troubleshooting/05.fail2ban.mdx:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "4. Save the file and reload the Fail2Ban configuration:\n"
msgstr "4. Sauvegardez le fichier et rechargez la configuration de Fail2Ban :\n"

